Text: EGF Offsite Cc From Ben Glisan Please be advised that the EGF Offsite is scheduled for Wednesday June th from pm and will be held in EBC Video conferencing will be available for those not able to attend in person Only VP and above will be invited to the Offsite Cocktails will follow directly after the meeting Place to be determined The meeting will be coordinated by Kelly Boots and Barry Schnapper Please advise if you will not be able to attend
Meeting Cc Fastow and Ben Glisan would like to meet with Greg Whalley and Mark Frevert this week if possible regarding Global Finance Support Please advise their availability Thank you
